title: Ep. - 412 - PAIGE DESORBO FROM WINTER HOUSE
description:
Kate reviews what to watch this weekend.

 

Paige Desorbo from Winter House on Bravo talks about the two weeks she spent in Vermont while cameras filmed, starting a relationship with Craig Conover from Southern Charm, and hailing from the same hometown as a cult leader.
